Package gw.api.domain.fundstracking

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PaymentItemsNarrative.Action
    Description for an action (either execute or reverse) that happened against a payment item.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FundsTrackingSwitch
    Enables and disables funds tracking.
    PaymentItemGroupsGenerator
    Class for generating PaymentItemGroup from the IFundsTracking plugin.
    PaymentItemsNarrative
    Tracks the PaymentItemActions the contexts in which they have occurred in the current bundle for use in creating PaymentItemGroup in the IFundsTracking plugin.
    PaymentItemsNarrative.Context
    Description for the context in which Actions and other Contexts may happen.
